import React, { Component } from 'react' import { Row, Col } from 'antd' class FAQS extends Component { render() { return (

FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS

How would you know what style to give me?
  • Our genies carefully review your Style Profile before mixing-and-matching fashion pieces for your box. So be sure to create your own, or our genies will be left guessing.
What if it doesn't fit me?
  • We have a One-Time Replacement Guarantee! (for Philippine orders only). Instructions will be emailed upon submission of your Returns Form.
How would you know what style to give me?
  • Our genies carefully review your Style Profile before mixing-and-matching fashion pieces for your box. So be sure to create your own, or our genies will be left guessing.
Do you accept Cash on Delivery as payment?
  • STYLEBOXES Since our stylists curate each box specifically for your Style Profile. E-GIFT CARDS gives you more than 35 payment centers. Chinabank or BPI for online transfers or over-the-counter deposits. GCash and PayMaya via 711,payment kiosks or mobile apps.
What are your available payment options?
  • STYLEBOXES for debit or credit cardholders. E-GIFT CARDS gives you more than 35 payment centers. Chinabank or BPI for online transfers or over-the-counter deposits. GCash and PayMaya via 711,payment kiosks or mobile apps.
How long will it take you to ship my order?
  • STYLEBOXES are shipped every 15th of the following month. E-GIFT CARDS are automatically sent via email..
What is the delivery lead time?
  • Metro Manila: 48 hours upon shipment
  • outside Metro Manila: 5 to 7 business days upon shipment
  • outside the Philippines: 14 to 21 business days upon shipment
Do you ship outside Metro Manila?
  • Yes - we ship nationwide!
Do you ship outside the Philippines?
  • Yes - additional freight costs will be emailed after order confirmation. We ship worldwide via FEDEX, DHL, UPS or EMS.
What is Shazuums?
  • Shazuums is how magical people say hello or bye, or simply the expression you give whenever your wish has been granted!
) } } export default FAQS
